      "side": 1,
      "message": "I add the observation (from the actual production code) into the commit msg.\n\nIt tells that this problem may occur if the object (shared_from_this) is already deleted before the callback (which is bound to std::bind_front) is yet invoked.\nThen, the value of `this` (which was passed to std::bind_front) may be dangling when the callback is invoked.",
